# Stripe Configuration
# Copy this file and set environment variables for your environment.
#
# Required environment variables:
#   STRIPE_SECRET_KEY       - Your Stripe secret key (sk_test_... or sk_live_...)
#   STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY  - Your Stripe publishable key (pk_test_... or pk_live_...)
#   STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET   - Webhook signing secret (whsec_...)
#
# Plan Price IDs (create in Stripe Dashboard > Products):
#   STRIPE_STARTER_PRICE_ID - Price ID for Starter plan ($49/mo)
#   STRIPE_GROWTH_PRICE_ID  - Price ID for Growth plan ($149/mo)
#
# For local development with Stripe CLI:
#   stripe listen --forward-to localhost:3000/webhooks/stripe
